<p><em><h1>How it works</em></h1><p>
<ol>
<h2>
<li>Thirty bills, that have been discussed in California in the last 3 years, will be displayed. </li>
<li>Each bill will display 4 options (<em> positive</em>, <em>negative</em>, <em>absence</em> and <em>absent </em>).</li>
<li>You have to choose one option for each bill displayed. </li>
<li>After you are done voting all of the bills, a table with the names of the representatives that have voted in coincidence or dissidence with your votes will be shown.</li>
</h2>
</ol>
